				<!-- Player info -->
				<h4>Important info</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>You must have a <b>mic</b> and communicate with your teammates when playing in Wecasual.</li>
					<li>Wecasual is for players who are <b>less than 4k MMR </b> (Case by case exceptions can be made).</li>
					<li>Wecasual plays on the <b>USE server</b>, and communication is done in <b>english</b>.</li>
					<!-- <li>Wecasual is in <b>free beta</b> right now!	<i>(Wecasual's full release will be $5/month)</i></li> -->
