						<h4 class = "py-1 col col-12">Please enter your teammate requests</h4>
						<div class = "py-1 col col-12">
							<ul>
								<li>You can request up to <b>4</b> teammates to play with.</li>
								<li>Enter the <b>Steam display names</b> of any players you would like to be on a team with. Blank entries will be ignored.</li>
